                                                            <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> a campaign that places calls without the aid of human agents. When the recipient answers a message is played and then call is disconnected. This is used for announcement recordings to be played to customers that have already opted to receive the call (school closings, prescription reminders, etc.). Also known as “robo-dialing”</span></p>
