                                                            <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                                <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">the basic module of Dialer360, allowing for outbound calls. A user will need to log into a campaign to be able to place or receive phone calls.</span></p>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1dbf24f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="1dbf24f" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
